PN,31201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe government's delay in publishing
OL,7,Fthe Defence Investment Plan (DIP) has
OL,8,Fundermined the UK's credibility with
OL,9,Fits allies and its ability to provide
OL,10,Fa stronger deterrent to its
OL,11,Fadversaries, say MPs.
OL,13,FIn a report into the Ministry of
OL,14,FDefence's 2024-25 accounts, the Public
OL,15,FAccounts Committee (PAC) of MPs warned
OL,16,Fthat the long delay to the DIP risks
OL,17,Fsquandering the opportunities provided
OL,18,Fby advances in technology, hindering
OL,19,Fthe government's attempts to modernise
OL,20,Fthe Armed Forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe DIP, which was originally due last
OL,7,Fyear, may now not be published until
OL,8,FJuly, shortly before a Nato summit.
OL,10,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, who chairs
OL,11,Fthe committee, said: "Those
OL,12,Fresponsible may argue there are good
OL,13,Freasons for the DIP's continuing
OL,14,Fabsence, but our report makes clear
OL,15,Fthat excuses to the effect of 'taking
OL,16,Fthe time to get the details right'
OL,17,Fsimply do not cut it.
OL,26,@sD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,F"Whatever the content of the DIP when
OL,7,Fit eventually does appear, the damage
OL,8,Ffrom its absence has been done ` to
OL,9,Fthe nation's credibility, to its
OL,10,Fsafety, to its armed forces, and to
OL,11,Fcertainty within its entire defence
OL,12,Findustrial base.
OL,14,F"Any government minister attempting to
OL,15,Fexplain away this delay to the DIP
OL,16,Fshould instead ask themselves what
OL,17,Fmessage the bureaucratic drift of the
OL,18,Fpast months has given to the public,
OL,19,Fas well as the UK's allies and its
OL,20,Fadversaries, and simply apologise."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe MoD "has not yet decided which
OL,7,Fcapabilities, infrastructure and
OL,8,Fpeople it requires to transform the
OL,9,Farmed forces to be warfighting-ready
OL,10,Fwithin the budget available" and "nor
OL,11,Fhas it secured the cross-government
OL,12,Fagreement that the plan needs".
OL,14,FA MoD spokesman said the Government is
OL,15,Fproviding a "generational increase" in
OL,16,Fdefence spending, with an extra #270
OL,17,Fbillion across this Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@IOUrD@\O]rD@bOUtD@^O]wD@MOUwD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe spokesman said: "The defence
OL,7,Finvestment plan will fix the outdated,
OL,8,Fovercommitted and underfunded
OL,9,Fprogramme we inherited.
OL,11,F"We are working hard to finalise it.
OL,12,FAs the Defence Secretary told
OL,13,FParliament this week, the Prime
OL,14,FMinister is determined to publish it
OL,15,Fbefore the Nato Summit."
OL,17,FMPs on the committee also raised
OL,18,Fconcerns over whether the Army's
OL,19,Ftroubled #6.3 billion Ajax armoured
OL,20,Fvehicle will ever be fit for use in
OL,21,Fcombat.
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe project has been dogged by
OL,7,Fconcerns about the impact of noise and
OL,8,Fvibration on the crew, and the Public
OL,9,FAccounts Committee warned there were
OL,10,F"unrealistic expectations" about how
OL,11,Fsoldiers would be able to safely
OL,12,Foperate the armoured vehicle in a war
OL,13,Fzone.
OL,15,FThe Ajax system was initially expected
OL,16,Fto enter into operation in 2017, but
OL,17,Fhas been repeatedly hit by setbacks
OL,18,Fover crew safety concerns.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe vehicle was finally cleared for
OL,7,Foperations in November last year, but
OL,8,Fwithin weeks, an exercise had to be
OL,9,Fhalted because soldiers experienced
OL,10,Fsymptoms linked to noise and vibration.
OL,12,FIn its report, the Public Accounts
OL,13,FCommittee said the Ministry of Defence
OL,14,F(MoD) asserted there were "no safety
OL,15,Fconcerns about Ajax provided it was
OL,16,Foperated and maintained correctly
OL,17,Fwithin its design parameters".
OL,26,@vD@[OUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FIt said soldiers had been instructed
OL,7,Fto carry out maintenance checks every
OL,8,Ftime they stop the vehicle, but the
OL,9,FMoD "did not explain the practicality
OL,10,Fof this for soldiers operating Ajax
OL,11,Ffor long periods in combat".
