PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FMPs were also critical of the MoD's
OL,7,F"ever-increasing nuclear expenditure",
OL,8,Fclaiming it made up 18% (#10.9
OL,9,Fbillion) of the defence budget in 2024-
OL,10,F25, and is expected to rise to up to
OL,11,F25% in the coming years, recommending
OL,12,Fmore detailed cost and performance
OL,13,Finformation be provided to parliament
OL,14,Ffor scrutiny.
OL,16,FThe report also highlighted the uptake
OL,17,Fin recruitment shown in statistics for
OL,18,Fthe year to October 2025, turning a
OL,19,Fcorner on years of dwindling
OL,20,Fapplications, with more people joining
OL,21,Fup than leaving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe MoD does not, however, know
OL,7,Fwhether these improvements are a
OL,8,Fresult of its own efforts or if it can
OL,9,Fsustain them; the committee
OL,10,Frecommended that work be done to
OL,11,Fidentify which recruitment methods had
OL,12,Fbeen successful so more effort can be
OL,13,Fapplied in these areas.
OL,15,FThe report's publication comes the
OL,16,Fsame day as the news that the Ministry
OL,17,Fof Defence (MoD) is developing a
OL,18,Fsubmarine maintenance recovery plan
OL,19,Famid reports that the Royal Navy's
OL,20,Fentire available fleet of hunter-
OL,21,Fkiller submarines is docked.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780902266
OL,3,CDelays in defence plan 'undermining'
OL,4,CUK with allies, say MPs
OL,6,FThe Mail on Sunday reported all five
OL,7,FAstute class submarines ` which are
OL,8,Fused to protect the Vanguard
OL,9,Fsubmarines which carry nuclear Trident
OL,10,Fmissiles ` are out of service while
OL,11,Fthey undergo maintenance and repair
OL,12,Fwork.
OL,14,FJust one day earlier, the MoD
OL,15,Fannounced a technical fault had been
OL,16,Fdiscovered on the HMS Prince of Wales,
OL,17,Fwhich also required maintenance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
